name: Ladybug Pram pegs
description: No longer will your baby blanket fall on the ground or get blown off. The “Pram peg” fits all prams and strollers, anything to make your life easier.  These easy to use pram pegs will add a decorative touch to your baby’s pram or stroller.  The perfect gift to top off your baby shower present.  “Pram pegs” comes in a set of four.
